  <brief_title>Effect of Vitamin D on Ventricular Remodeling in Patients With Acute Myocardial Infarction (VITDAMI)</brief_title>
  <acronym>VITDAMI</acronym>
  <official_title>Multicentric, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Clinical Trial to Assess the Effect of Vitamin D on Ventricular Remodeling in Patients With Acute Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
