  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the effect of calcifediol on left ventricular remodeling, mineral metabolism, plasma
      levels of several prognostic biomarkers and on endothelial function after an anterior
      myocardial infarction.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
